pip3 install spyder

如果安装完成没有桌面图标:
nano ~/.local/share/applications/spyder.desktop

[Desktop Entry]
Name=Spyder
Comment=Scientific Python Development Environment
Exec=/home/wei/.pyenv/shims/spyder  # 或使用绝对路径：$(which spyder)
Icon=/home/wei/.local/share/applications/spyder.jpg
Terminal=false
Type=Application
Categories=Development;IDE;
StartupWMClass=Spyder
